Fine Organic Industries Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 08/05/2025 inter alia to consider and approve  the following matters:

1) Audited Financial results (both standalone and consolidated) for the quarter and financial year ended March 31 2025; 
2) Recommendation of Dividend if any for the financial year ended March 31 2025.
